      "description": "S1257L £150,000 in 2024-25 reaches the 48% top band, which per the Scottish Rate Resolution starts at £125,140 of TAXABLE income. Month-1 derivation: PA fully tapered to 0; taxable 12,500/mo; monthly boundaries ceil(2306/12)=193, 1166, 2591, 5203, ceil(125140/12)=10429; tax = 193x19% + 973x20% + 1425x21% + 2612x42% + 5226x45% + 2071x48% = 36.67+194.60+299.25+1097.04+2351.70+994.08 = 4,973.34/mo (59,680.08/yr).",
